    <section class="intro">
        <div class="intro-body">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
                        <h1 class="brand-heading">Flashcards</h1>
                        <p class="intro-text">Like a wave in the physical world, may this be your guide to the infinite ocean of knowledge which pervades all; And your learning be as boisterous and unyielding.</p>
                        <div class="page-scroll">
                            <a href="#about" class="btn btn-circle">
                                <i class="fa fa-angle-double-down animated"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>Directives</h2>
                <p>The Game is simple. Pick a deck. Cards will be chosen at random. Guess.</p>
                <p>Wait. Don't guess. Learn.</p>
                <p>Learn away little one; Learn away...</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="download" class="content-section text-center">
        <div class="download-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">

                <div class="container" style="max-width:400px">
                    <div class="row" style="text-align:center;">
                                <%= yield %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="container content-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
                <h2>Got Feedback? Harumph!</h2>
                <p>People often tell us, WOWZERS!, your site is b(with a capital B)-eautiful... There is probably nothing that you can do better, and any input from you would just be taking away from the gift to human-kind that is this page.</p>
                <p>Well, they're probably right. But... since we're oh so very humble, and... mindful of the people's need to express their thoughts and be heard. You can shoot us an email which we'll never read, but will pretend to care about, so that you, our beloved user, will feel swept up in our loving embrace.</p>
                <p>feedback@gmail.com</p>
                <ul class="list-inline banner-social-buttons">
                    <li><a href="https://twitter.com/" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Twitter</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/CharlieTruong/sinatra_flash_card" class="btn btn-default btn-lg"><i class="fa fa-github fa-fw"></i> <span class="network-name">Github</span></a>
